  "firstAcquaintance": "A well-proportioned winged-kin girl who always greets everyone with a smile, then beautifully messes up everything she tries to do.",
  "personality": "Like most winged-kin, she has a lively and kind personality. She's a natural charmer, and laughter always fills the air wherever she is.",
  "like": "Black tea",
  "familiarData": "Noel was born after the great war. The kingdom had already fallen and retreated to the north, and the Holy Mother Church could barely take care of itself. So without receiving the full winged-kin heritage, Noel was pushed into the role of shrine maiden by villagers at a young age, in a remote church in the countryside.\nOriginally living in hiding with winged-kin followers in the remote wilderness, Noel was attacked by slave hunters and sold at the slave market. Whether by luck or not, Noel was purchased by the guild shortly after arriving at the slave market, without experiencing torture or conditioning.\nLike all winged-kin, Noel is completely hopeless at daily life. Though she's always energetic and eager to help others, she couldn't do much before because she was protected by the Holy Mother Church's followers. After becoming a slave and being bought by the guild, her desire to help people grew much stronger. But she always overestimates her own abilities, which gives everyone quite a headache...",
